==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: boogie
<hw>boog"ie</hw> <pr>(b⟦oocr⟧g"⟦emac⟧)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To do
a lively dance, often with the two partners not touching, to the
accompaniment of rock music.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>boogie-woogie</ent>⟦br⟧
